Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幼女赞记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疗养腻了没
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对想太多的自己是一个很好的反省机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息了这么长时间应该很闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么想要的东西么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 喝故乡的啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也有点困难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没法弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际可能并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某个地方似藏着大量的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可信赖的情报来源
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以拜托你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了可怜的副队长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去为您取得巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 哪里藏着大量巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少校的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少校的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能…不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:00:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:00:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对个毛线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是知道是少校的东西的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.49,0:01:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这气氛我说不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对个毛线啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就要鼓起勇气和少校说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疗养中的拜斯中尉想要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请分点巧克力给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.09,0:01:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此请求一下怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.01,0:01:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是为了部下的话少校也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少校珍藏的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能稍微分点给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少校 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少校你还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢甜品没有任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.11,0:01:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么想要巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疗养中的拜斯中尉非常喜欢吃巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.74,0:01:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,务必作为疗养的慰问
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙喜欢巧克力么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看他那样可不像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会准备点的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少校那张脸意外的说了点可爱的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是得到了巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我倒是很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了 拜斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您身体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢列布里亚科夫少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要吃一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以么？

